name: User can filter the off plan products by Unit price range

steps.name: When Click on the sign in
When Log in to the page.
And Click on “off plan” at the left side menu.
Then Verify the right page opens.
And Filter the products by price range from 1200000 to 2000000 AED.
And Verify the price in all cards is inside the range (1200000 - 2000000).

fullName: Features of off-plan page: User can filter the off plan products by Unit price range
